** This project is alpha **

This project provides metaclass propagation along with class inheritance structures.
This project use closer-mop and modify c2mop:ensure-class-usgin-class by around-method so
it can conflict with some libraries modifing same method.

Usage:
  1. download from git.
  2. move the directory to quicklisp local-project directory.
  3. (ql:quickload :meta-propagate)
  4. (metap:register-m1-m2-pair your-class your-metaclass)

  See singleton-mixin (https://github.com/

